law.text:
The Program shall provide business assistance services that:
determine whether the employer's specific needs are best met by training, other types of assistance, or a combination of services;
identify the availability of existing training programs that may be adapted to meet the employer's needs;
identify the resources the employer may provide to support the training, including:
equipment;
facilities; and
materials;
identify or develop appropriate curricula; and
determine the most cost-effective approach to meeting training needs.
